                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290611-296-off1562 t18290611-296-cd1563"></join>, 1 cloak, value 15s.; 1 veil, value 12s.; 1 bonnet, value 12s., and 1 pair of stockings, value 1s., the goods of 
                     
